    "body": "btw, meant to ask this for a while - why doesn't Rust have an official LLVM repo? (and libuv too for that matter)   Having one would remove the need to re-point submodule origin each time someone does LLVM fix, and it would also enable submittal/review of PRs, just like it's done for the main repo.\n",
