    "body": "It's pretty much agreed upon that having a rust organization on github (#9343) would be a good idea. That would indeed be the house for all our dependencies like llvm, gyp, libuv, etc. I think the reason it hasn't been done is that it just hasn't been done, there isn't really a particularly fundamental reason it hasn't been done yet.\n",
